  },
  {
    question: "How do you handle older kitchens and bathrooms?",
    answer: "Blossomwood kitchens range from beautifully preserved vintage style to completely renovated modern spaces. Same with bathrooms - some retain charming original tile, others are fully updated. We adapt our approach to what you have, using appropriate products and techniques for both vintage and contemporary surfaces."
  },
  {
    question: "Can you work around our home-based business or work-from-home schedule?",
    answer: "Many Blossomwood residents work from home or run small businesses from their properties. We can absolutely work around your schedule - clean during specific hours, avoid your office space during calls, or focus on certain rooms while you work in others. We're flexible and understand the work-from-home lifestyle."
