  {
    question: "Do you serve the rental properties and Airbnbs in the Blossomwood area?",
    answer: "Yes! Blossomwood's walkability to downtown makes it popular for short-term rentals. We provide turnover cleaning for Airbnb hosts and property owners, as well as regular maintenance for rental properties. Quick turnarounds, attention to guest-ready details, and reliable scheduling keep your rental performing well."
  }
];

